{
  "id": "adv_event_2211_01_01",
  "title": "幽霊旅館？",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（今、ⅢXはライブツアーで各地を回っている）\n（彼女達は人気を取り戻しつつあって、会場も満員……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "( Right now‚ IIIX is on a live tour‚ traveling from place to place. )\n( The girls are gradually regaining their popularity‚\nand the venues are packed… )",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 9.4440589904,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 15000
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（……なんだが、様子がおかしい。もう宿を出ないと）\n（いけないのに、三人ともまだ起きてこない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…Something's not right‚ though.\nWe need to check out of the hotel soon.）\n（But the three of them haven't woken up yet‚\neven though they should have by now.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.9333333333,
      "endTime": 17.1749431928,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-03.m4a",
          "delay": 8733.3333334
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（これは……荷物はめちゃくちゃに散らかってるし）\n（あの仲が悪いスリクスが、抱き合って寝てるだと！？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（This is… The luggage is scattered everywhere messily.）\n（That IIIX‚ known for their bad relationships‚\nare sleeping while hugging each other!?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.4666666667,
      "endTime": 26.6914893921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "みなさん、起きて下さい\n昨日の夜、一体何があったんですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone‚ please wake up.\nWhat on earth happened last night?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.0666666667,
      "endTime": 31.9427585733,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――前日、午後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Prior day‚ afternoon",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.1333333333,
      "endTime": 34.4133333524,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1399.9999999999986
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_01-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと～、何このボロっちい宿\nkana、ツアー真っ最中のアイドル様なんですけど？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh‚ what's with this shabby inn?\nKana‚ I'm an idol in the middle of a tour‚ you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.2333333333,
      "endTime": 45.3237955174,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.7
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_01-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "あなたが「温泉入りたい、でないと殺す」とか\nわがまま言ったからでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's because you said \"I want to go to a hot spring‚\nor I'll kill you‚\" didn't you?\nIt's all because of your selfishness.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.5333333333,
      "endTime": 51.858288967300005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_01-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "温泉と、一泊あたりの予算の両方を満たすのが\nこの宿しかなかったんでしょうね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Considering both the hot spring\nand the budget for one night's stay‚\nThis was probably the only inn available…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.0666666667,
      "endTime": 57.8427126583,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_01-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "これだから、ちっちゃい事務所ってさあ～！\n……あ、なんか天井のとこお札まで貼ってあるし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is why I can't stand small agencies!\n…Oh‚ there are even talismans stuck to the ceiling.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.0333333333,
      "endTime": 66.383713586,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_01-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "ボロいし、いかにもじめ～っとしてるし\nこの宿、もしかして心霊スポットかなんかじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's run-down and feels all damp and chilly.\nIs this place some kind of haunted spot or something?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.6,
      "endTime": 74.69114986609999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_01-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "何、馬鹿なこと言ってるの\nこのご時世、幽霊なんている訳ないでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you talking about? That's ridiculous.\nIn this day and age‚ there's no such thing as ghosts.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.9,
      "endTime": 81.64681887469999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_01-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "ふ～ん。幽霊が怖いとか\n山田さんってば、か～わいい～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmmm. Being scared of ghosts‚\nYamada-san‚ you're sooo cute~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.8333333333,
      "endTime": 89.4049522909,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_01-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "だから毎度毎度、山田って呼ぶなってば！！\nそれと別に怖がってなんかいないわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For the umpteenth time‚ stop calling me Yamada!!\nAnd I'm not scared at all!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.6,
      "endTime": 96.7407517684,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_01-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "これだから経済誌読まないお子様は困るわ\n歴史のある旅館の再生ビジネスが今流行ってるんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is why kids who don't read\nfinancial magazines are troublesome.\nThe business of reviving old inns is trending right now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.9333333333,
      "endTime": 105.1029828596,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_01-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "この宿だって、建物は古いけど立地は悪くないし\nうまくやって儲け話に一口噛めないかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if this place is old‚ its location isn't bad.\nMaybe we could get in on a lucrative deal?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.3333333333,
      "endTime": 114.6470451852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_01-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "あっそ、勝手に出資して大損すれば",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sure‚ go ahead and invest‚ and then take a huge loss.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.8666666667,
      "endTime": 119.5337416331,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_01-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "……はあ\n……二人ともやめなさい、宿の人に聞こえるでしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…sigh.\n…Both of you‚ please stop. People in the inn can hear you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.7333333333,
      "endTime": 125.0777843839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_01-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "ともかく、チェックアウトは明日の朝八時よ\nくれぐれも寝坊しないようにね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyway‚ check-out is at 8 o'clock tomorrow morning.\nBe sure not to oversleep.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.2666666667,
      "endTime": 130.71605978009998,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8933.333333299985
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9266.66666659999
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_01-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "まだ夕方だし、結構時間あるなー……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's still early evening‚ so we have plenty of time…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.9,
      "endTime": 135.3507258415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 135.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_01-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "私は、一昨日のライブの動画を見直さないと\n完璧なステージのために妥協は出来ないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I need to review the video from\nthe day before yesterday's live performance.\nI can't compromise for a perfect stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.5666666667,
      "endTime": 141.8311122112,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 142
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_01-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "よろしくね～、miho\n私は、露天風呂に行ってくるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "See you later‚ Miho.\nI'm going to the open-air bath.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142,
      "endTime": 146.40951107030003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 146.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_01-kan007.m4a",
